This is Perl module WWW::Lingr::Simple.

INSTALLATION

WWW::Lingr::Simple installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % git clone https://Likk@github.com/Likk/WWW-Lingr-Simple.git ./

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % cd ./WWW-Lingr-Simple
    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

WWW::Lingr::Simple documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc WWW::Lingr::Simple

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

